sentence: list the nonstop flights on wednesday june second from miami to baltimore arriving in baltimore between eleven fifteen a m and twelve forty five p m
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v0.flight_id||'"', v0.stops, '"'||v1.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v3.airport_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v5.days_code||'"', '"'||v6.day_name||'"',
 v6.year, v6.month_number, v6.day_number, v0.arrival_time FROM flight v0,
 airport_service v1, city v2, airport_service v3,
 city v4, days v5, date_day v6 
WHERE ((v0.stops =  0) 
AND (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code)

AND (((v0.to_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) 
AND (v4.city_name = 'BALTIMORE'))) AND (((v0.flight_days = ANY v5.days_code) 
AND ((v5.day_name = ANY v6.day_name) 
AND (((v6.year =  1993) AND (v6.month_number =  6)) 
AND (v6.day_number =  2)))) AND ((v0.arrival_time >=  1115) 
AND (v0.arrival_time <=  1245))))));
